{
  "stem": "3277.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rifle, used to push me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hit me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Go, go, go, go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I limped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In such conditions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got to go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people-- oh yes, and I-- and that's what I said before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People used to die from malnutrition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First, they used to-- as I told before, they used to get swollen legs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Soon this came through the body.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They died without any-- any pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No medical center.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a guy who used to look at you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, no-- he was not a-- not a doctor, even not-- not even a nurse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just he was the lucky guy, they let him be like a nurse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was not a nurse even.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No medicine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No medicine, no-- no doctors, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You would-- listen, as I told you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got to work seven days a week, and the horses six days a week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which means you were just a number and just a-- an animal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not a-- everything was un-human conditions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, if my English would be better, if this was my-- my native language, I would have explained it-- if I could say this in-- everything in Polish or in Yiddish, it would sound completely different, and worse.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because-- because treated people like animals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Un-human conditions.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I wouldn't say that just to us, everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even those Russians, they suffered, those-- those people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, what once happened that one of our people, he was out of shape, completely.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what happened, when we went out, they made signs where we can walk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you go out of this place, he-- that guy got the right to shoot to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one-- one of our guys, he was out of-- he was completely out.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
